              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>A deductive system <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {D}]]></fr:tex> is called a <fr:em>preduploid</fr:em> when every object <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A\in \mathcal {D}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-0045.xml" title="Polarized object" addr="jms-0045" type="local">polarized</fr:link>.</fr:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
